p under their name in different classes.\n\n=== ERA ===\n\n*Baldwinsville ERA, Baldwinsville, NY\n*Central Square ERA, Central Square, NY\n*Laurens ERA, Laurens, NY\n*Pinewood Elementary, Schenectady, NY\n*Phoenix ERA, Phoenix, NY\n*Southern Tier ERA, Endicott, NY\n\n=== Cadet ===\n*Albany City Cadet, Albany, NY\n*Arlington Cadet, LaGrangeville, NY\n*Jordan-Elbridge Cadet, Jordan, NY\n*Laurens Jr. Jaguars, Laurens, NY\n*Mohonasen JV, Schenectady, NY\n*New Hartford JV, New Hartford, NY\n*Pine Grove MS, East Syracuse, NY\n*Shenendehowa Cadet, Clifton Park, NY\n*Vestal Jr., Vestal, NY\n*Victor Cadet, Victor, NY\n*Westmoreland Jr., Westmoreland, NY\n\n=== SRA ===\n\n*Baldwinsville HS JV, Baldwinsville, NY\n*Central Square JV, Central Square, NY\n*Homer HS, Homer, NY\n*Horseheads HS, Horseheads, NY\n*Liverpool HS JV, Liverpool, NY\n*Oswego HS, Oswego, NY\n*Shenendehowa SRA, Clifton Park, NY\n*Sherburne-Earlville HS, Sherburne, NY\n*Vestal Sr, Vestal, NY\n*West Genesee HS , Camillus, NY\n\n=== IRA ===\n*Cicero-North Syracuse HS Northstars Jr.\n*Greater Johnstown Amethyst, Johnstown, NY\n*Southern Tier IRA, Endicott, NY\n\n=== IAA ===\n*Dare, Binghamton, NY\n*Excelsior, Troy, NY\n\n=== SA3 ===\n\n*Albany HS, Albany, NY\n*Corning-Painted Post HS, Corning, NY\n*Norwich HS, Norwich, NY\n*Phoenix HS JV, Phoenix, NY\n*RFA Black Knights, Rome, NY\n*Westmoreland HS Sr., Westmoreland, NY\n\n=== SA2 ===\n*Baldwinsville Var, Baldwinsville, NY\n*Cicero-North Syracuse Northstars JV, Cicero, NY\n*Greater Johnstown HS Amethyst Gold, Johnstown, NY\n*Jordan-Elbrdge HS Var., Jordan, NY\n*Laurens Jaguars, Laurens, NY\n*New Hartford HS Var., New Hartford, NY\n\n=== SA1 ===\n\n*Central Square Var. Central Square, NY\n*East Syracuse-Minoa, East Syracuse, NY\n\n*Liverpool HS Var., Liverpool, NY\n*Mohonasen Var., Schenectady, NY\n*Shenendehowa HS JV, Clifton Park, NY\n\n=== IA ===\n\n* Introspective (Binghamton, NY)\n*Oxford Academy, Oxford, NY\n\n=== SO ===\n*Arlington Admirals, LaGrangeville, 