 Academy Awards|1958]]\n|''[[Witness for the Prosecution (1957 film)|Witness for the Prosecution]]''\n|[[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n|{{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1958|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|accessdate=December 17, 2019|title=The 30th Academy Awards}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[32nd Academy Awards|1960]]\n|rowspan=2|''[[Some Like It Hot]]''\n|[[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n|{{nom}}\n|rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1960|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|accessdate=December 17, 2019|title=The 32nd Academy Awards}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Academy Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Screenplay]]\n|{{nom}}{{efn|name=Diamond|Shared with [[I. A. L. Diamond]]}}\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[33rd Academy Awards|1961]]\n|rowspan=3|''[[The Apartment]]''\n|[[Academy Award for Best Picture|Best Picture]]\n|{{won}}\n|rowspan=3 style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1961|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|accessdate=December 17, 2019|title=The 33rd Academy Awards}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[Academy Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n|{{won}}{{efn|name=Diamond}}\n|-\n|[[39th Academy Awards|1967]]\n|''[[The Fortune Cookie]]''\n|[[Academy Award for Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n|{{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1967|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|accessdate=December 17, 2019|title=The 39th Academy Awards}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[60th Academy Awards|1988]]\n|\n|[[Irving G. Thalberg Memorial Award]]\n|{{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1988|publisher=Academy of Motion P